OL,3,CWheelchair user had 'three panic
OL,4,Cattacks' after frustrating London
OL,5,Ctrain journey
OL,7,FZara Beth was looking forward to
OL,8,Fseeing her grandmother in northwest
OL,9,FLondon before heading to France on
OL,10,Fholiday the next day.
OL,12,FShe has autism, Tourette syndrome, as
OL,13,Fwell as chronic illnesses and uses a
OL,14,Fwheelchair to travel and help manage
OL,15,Fher symptoms.
