OL,3,CWheelchair user had 'three panic
OL,4,Cattacks' after frustrating London
OL,5,Ctrain journey
OL,7,FThe 20-year-old had planned her London
OL,8,Fcommute far in advance to include
OL,9,Faccessible routes. Having commuted
OL,10,Ffrom Manchester, she intended to
OL,11,Ftravel north on the Thameslink from St
OL,12,FPancras to visit her relative.
OL,14,FWhen when she arrived, the lift was
OL,15,Fbroken. She said: "My heart just sunk."
OL,17,F"There are so many people that need to
OL,18,Fuse the lift and having it out of
OL,19,Forder really impacts everybody and I
OL,20,Fdon't know how they can leave it for
OL,21,Fso long without fixing it."
