OL,5,Ctrain journey
OL,7,FStaff told her to get the tube to
OL,8,FFarringdon from Kings Cross, then get
OL,9,Fthe tube back to St Pancras so she
OL,10,Fwould be on the "right side of the
OL,11,Fplatform underneath" so she could
OL,12,Fchange trains.
OL,14,FBut this was difficult to navigate on
OL,15,Fher own, especially with so many
OL,16,Fpeople and signs being difficult to
OL,17,Fsee. When Zara reached the tube she
OL,18,Fhad a panic attack, finding it
OL,19,F"overwhelming."
