OL,4,Cattacks' after frustrating London
OL,5,Ctrain journey
OL,7,FShe said: "I'm autistic, so change is
OL,8,Fdifficult. Navigating, communicating,
OL,9,Fit's all more difficult than usual and
OL,10,Fit takes so much energy."
OL,12,FA member of staff at King's Cross told
OL,13,Fher to go to Farringdon and directed
OL,14,Fher to the relevant platform, but when
OL,15,Fshe got to Farringdon and took the
OL,16,Ftube back to Kings Cross, she arrived
OL,17,Fback at the same platform and was back
OL,18,Fto square one.
OL,26,@oD@KOUrD@YO]
