OL,4,Cattacks' after frustrating London
OL,5,Ctrain journey
OL,7,FStaff then told her that she had to
OL,8,Ffully exit the station barriers at
OL,9,FFarringdon and change platforms, but
OL,10,Fthis wasn't previously clarified. When
OL,11,Fshe visited the information desk,
OL,12,Fstaff told her both Farringdon and her
OL,13,Fend destination would be step-free,
OL,14,Fbut staff on the platform said her
OL,15,Fstop was not actually accessible and
OL,16,Fthey could not take her there.
