OL,4,Cattacks' after frustrating London
OL,5,Ctrain journey
OL,7,FShe was offered a taxi, but was told
OL,8,Fit might take over an hour, and Zara
OL,9,Frejected this due to fears of trying
OL,10,Fto navigate back and missing her
OL,11,Fmorning train to France the next day.
OL,13,FStaff quickly put her on the next
OL,14,Ftrain before she could fully decide
OL,15,Fher plan of action. She realised she
OL,16,Fwouldn't be able to get back in the
OL,17,Fmorning and began to panic. Her mum
OL,18,Ftexted saying "don't go to grandmas"
OL,19,Fand told her to get off at the next
OL,20,Fstop and head back to London.
