OL,3,CWheelchair user had 'three panic
OL,4,Cattacks' after frustrating London
OL,5,Ctrain journey
OL,7,FFeeling frustrated about cancelling
OL,8,Fplans, Zara said: "It's really
OL,9,Fannoying because I hate letting people
OL,10,Fdown and it's more annoying when it's
OL,11,Fnot my fault.
OL,13,F"Just because I can't get down the
OL,14,Fstairs or because I can't just step up
OL,15,Fonto the train, it meant that the
OL,16,Fwhole journey was cancelled."
OL,18,FAt this point Zara had reached Kentish
OL,19,FTown, a station that does not have
OL,20,Fstep free access, and a passenger
OL,21,Fhelped her get off the train.
