OL,5,Ctrain journey
OL,7,FThere were no train staff on the
OL,8,Fplatform and no lift. She was stuck.
OL,10,F40 minutes after crying on the phone
OL,11,Fto support, a member of staff arrived
OL,12,Fwith a ramp.
OL,14,FShe said: "I was exhausted. I'd
OL,15,Fcommunicated with so many people,
OL,16,Fwhich I find difficult. I felt like
OL,17,Fpeople weren't listening to me.
OL,26,@vD@KOU
