OL,3,CWheelchair user had 'three panic
OL,4,Cattacks' after frustrating London
OL,5,Ctrain journey
OL,7,F"It was really frustrating because I
OL,8,Fjust wish someone could have properly
OL,9,Fplanned out the route and actually
OL,10,Fmade sure I could get there instead of
OL,11,Fjust telling me to do something and
OL,12,Fthen leaving me."
OL,14,FIn a statement, a spokesperson for
OL,15,FGovia Thameslink Railway apologised
OL,16,Fand said: "The wellbeing of all of our
OL,17,Fpassengers is extremely important,
OL,18,Fespecially those who are disabled, and
OL,19,Fwe will be making contact with Zara so
OL,20,Fthat we can investigate exactly what
OL,21,Fhappened."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@QO]}D@JO]
