OL,5,Ctrain journey
OL,7,FShe eventually got on the Thameslink
OL,8,Fback to Farringdon, then back to St
OL,9,FPancras where she had to pay for a
OL,10,Fhotel.
OL,12,FThe journey, which was supposed to
OL,13,Fcost #4.65 with a Railcard, cost her
OL,14,F#30 due to the amount of train
OL,15,Fbarriers she passed through.
OL,17,FShe said: "That was kind of a kick in
OL,18,Fthe shins when I didn't get anywhere
OL,19,Fand it was quite a really stressful
OL,20,Fjourney that caused so much like
OL,21,Femotional panic for me."
