OL,7,F"Our vision is a London where everyone
OL,8,Fcan move around the city safely and
OL,9,Fcomfortably, and while we provide an
OL,10,Festablished turn-up-and-go service and
OL,11,Fhave taken steps to make our network
OL,12,Fmore accessible, we know that there is
OL,13,Fstill much work to be done."
OL,15,FTFL's Equity in Motion plan aims to
OL,16,Fdeliver more than 80 network
OL,17,Fimprovements including Customer
OL,18,FService and Disability Equality
OL,19,Ftraining for staff.
