OL,7,FZara said even stations that say
OL,8,Fthey're "accessible" have issues
OL,9,Fbecause "a lot of them have lifts and
OL,10,Fthey're often broken, and they take so
OL,11,Flong to repair them."
OL,13,FA Network Rail spokesperson said:
OL,14,F"We're very sorry to Zara and other
OL,15,Fstation visitors who have been
OL,16,Finconvenienced by the fault with this
OL,17,Flift at London St Pancras.
OL,19,F"The parts have been ordered and we
OL,20,Faim to have the lift back in service
OL,21,Fas soon as possible.
